 the fiber of a definable subset\n$S$ of $M^{m+n}$ at $b \\in M^m$. We introduce the notion of multi-cells and\ndemonstrate that any definable set is a finite union of multi-cells in the\ncourse of the proof of the above theorem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 3 Apr 2021 04:12:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-08"}
